---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Bold Signs, Bigger Impact – Your B2B Signage Partner</h1>
<p><b>UK Sign Manufacturing & Dropshipping – From Neon to Lightboxes</b></p>			
<p>
				
At ContractSignage.co.uk, we manufacture and dropship high-quality signage for B2B sign companies across the UK. Established in 1989 and based on the northeast coast of Yorkshire, we have over three decades of expertise in the sign and print industry, producing everything from hand-blown glass neon signs to printed lightboxes, illuminated lettering, and large-format branding solutions. As a trusted UK-based trade supplier, we offer white-label signage services, ensuring your clients receive premium products without the need for in-house production.



			</p>
<p><b>Seamless Dropshipping – Premium Signs, Delivered Direct</b></p>	
			<p>
				
We make it easy for you to scale your signage business with our UK-based dropshipping service. Whether your clients need vibrant neon installations, sleek acrylic lettering, or custom LED lightboxes, we handle everything from manufacturing to direct delivery—branded with your business details. No need to invest in stock or manage logistics; we provide a hassle-free way to offer bespoke signage solutions with fast turnaround times and consistent quality.
			</p>
<p><b>Your Reliable UK Signage Partner</b></p>	

			<p>
With over 30 years of industry experience, ContractSignage.co.uk has built a reputation for expert craftsmanship, high-quality materials, and reliable service. From traditional hand-crafted neon to modern printed and illuminated signage, we support B2B sign companies with scalable production, trade pricing, and seamless logistics. Whether you're fulfilling single custom orders or large-scale contracts, our streamlined process ensures reliability and efficiency. Partner with us today to offer premium signage without the overheads.</p>
			<h1>Some of the signage we specialise in</h1>
			
<ul>
				<li>Hand-blown Glass Neon <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li>LED Faux Neon<code>src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li>3D Letters <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li>Acrylic Boxes <code>src/content/blog/</code></li>
				<li>Printed Lightboxes <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>read the docs
				</a> or <a href="https://astro.build/chat">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
					href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
					>astro-blog-template
				</a> by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
